query:
SELECT 
    v.id as venda_id,
    v.formandoId,
    f.id as formando_id_real,
    f.turmaId,
    CASE 
        WHEN f.turmaId IS NULL THEN 'SEM TURMA - EXCLUIR'
        ELSE 'COM TURMA - MANTER'
    END as acao
FROM vendas v 
LEFT JOIN formandos f ON v.formandoId = f.id
WHERE v.dataVenda BETWEEN '2026-06-14 00:00:00' AND '2026-06-15 23:59:59'
  AND v.excluido = 0
ORDER BY v.id
